flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 83: Risk Register Monitoring and Mitigation Escalation Workflow

  Intake[Risk identified]
  Score[Score likelihood and impact]
  Assign[Assign owner and mitigation plan]
  Mitigate[Execute mitigation actions]
  Residual[Residual risk review]
  Review[Periodic status review]
  Status{Risk resolved?}

  Close[Close risk and archive knowledge capture]
  EscalationCheck{High impact and unresolved?}
  Escalate[Escalate to leadership]
  Action[Execute escalated mitigation actions]

  Intake --> Score --> Assign --> Mitigate --> Residual --> Review --> Status
  Status -- Yes --> Close
  Status -- No --> EscalationCheck

  EscalationCheck -- Yes --> Escalate --> Action --> Review
  EscalationCheck -- No --> Assign
